snippet.title: Live Coding: Game of Life in Python w/ Pygame
snippet.description:
Today let's build a simple version of John Conway's Game of Life, an awesome cellular automaton simulation! Learn more about it at https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conway%27s_Game_of_Life
